title: President Murmu conferred Timor-Leste's highest civilian award for her efforts in public service, education
description: President Murmu conferred Timor-Leste's highest civilian award for her efforts in public service, education The award was conferred by President José Ramos-Horta of Timor-Leste for her achievements in public service and dedication to education, social welfare and empowerment of women.
